t":"哈哈哈，他感觉不光能写歌还挺能摸的，不过现在好像也不怎么管事了","createdAt":"2024-03-26T09:59:38"},{"id":"01963dec-e5f3-7377-8dcf-5b7a0bef34de","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7016,"content":"发工资比承诺的时间晚半个多月，定期提薪体检等福利待遇都没兑现，内部组织架构混乱，运营困难领导也不上心，本来定薪就比较低，还想方设法扣工资，不得不说国企公关能力就是强，其他平台但凡有吐槽的几天就删了，负面信息基本查不到，外面看一片欣欣向荣，实则内部一地鸡毛。","createdAt":"2024-03-27T15:13:12"},{"id":"01963dec-e636-7385-980e-0f94589f94ba","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1711,"content":"哈哈哈，钱全拿去公关了，没干正事","createdAt":"2024-03-27T15:21:04"},{"id":"01963dec-e63b-72df-ae3d-55bac68cf9f4","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7026,"content":"确实，在职的一个人要干很多人的活，招新人目前基本上也只招实习生了，年会的时候跟院长反馈，得到的回复就是克服困难~","createdAt":"2024-03-28T10:31:35"},{"id":"01963dec-e67e-719c-88ad-a582ab05433b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1711,"content":"哈哈哈，院长感觉不怎么管事呢，各种时候找不到人，有事还得找副院长，但也基本都在画饼","createdAt":"2024-03-29T14:25:33"},{"id":"01963dec-e687-703b-9698-fda7a1c51111","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7240,"content":"啊？","createdAt":"2024-05-27T21:05:38"},{"id":"01963dec-e6cc-7160-974d-d56b756dc8d5","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":6458,"content":"z怎么？","createdAt":"2024-05-30T11:18:03"},{"id":"01963dec-e6d1-7175-9144-9cc037f7b5a5","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7425,"content":"听上去这么叼的单位平台都能这么垃圾，我真的怀疑济南到底有没有好公司了","createdAt":"2024-06-20T19:48:12"},{"id":"01963dec-e683-71f8-9e2c-cbbd1e496afe","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":6458,"content":"那边情况怎么样了?我也在科技园上班。","createdAt":"2024-08-22T13:53:55"},{"id":"01963dec-e714-70e9-9c6b-59e1b846cd2c","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3703,"content":"是朝九晚五吗","createdAt":"2025-03-05T09:58:39"},{"id":"01963dec-e75f-70b6-a304-e33bbd77b7da","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":6434,"content":"啊？连工资都不发了？","createdAt":"2025-03-05T10:34:23"},{"id":"01963dec-e75a-73c4-b76f-d4e00f44fe6f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3383,"content":"是的，朝九晚五","createdAt":"2025-03-05T15:41:35"},{"id":"01963dec-e7a4-7256-9ede-2f18bcefae46","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22724,"content":"不至于，降薪了","createdAt":"2025-04-08T13:12:05"},{"id":"01963dec-e7a9-7296-a022-05d17b996e16","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22724,"content":"这边十五号之后发上个月工资","createdAt":"2025-04-08T15:01:21"},{"id":"01963dec-e7ae-7108-8b47-44a9a396be1b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":4087,"content":"发不出工资很正常，海康 都在降薪优化。只有领导是正式工，下面员工待遇和人家头头有啥关系  欠薪也拖欠不了人家的，都这样情况。哪里都一样。","createdAt":"2025-04-09T09:41:57"},{"id":"01963dec-e508-731f-ac0b-178bdf7cd432","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22724,"content":"这不是正经国企吧，卸磨杀驴也挺严重的，小私企作风","createdAt":"2025-04-12T16:03:56"},{"id":"01981620-6b04-71e1-ad9e-af8f49b5ae3c","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":25759,"content":"挺了解呀","createdAt":"2025-07-17T10:04:40"},{"id":"01981622-4788-700c-bb1f-3fde5468607e","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":25759,"content":"摸鱼小王子，私下都喊大S","createdAt":"2025-07-17T10:06:42"}]